<Link id="l00054" /><CodeLine lineNumber="54"><Highlight kind="comment">    /// The following field is used for ByteSize for non-implicit&#95;const</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00055" /><CodeLine lineNumber="55"><Highlight kind="comment">    /// attributes and as value for implicit&#95;const ones, indicated by</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00056" /><CodeLine lineNumber="56"><Highlight kind="comment">    /// Form == DW&#95;FORM&#95;implicit&#95;const.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00057" /><CodeLine lineNumber="57"><Highlight kind="comment">    /// The following cases are distinguished:</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00058" /><CodeLine lineNumber="58"><Highlight kind="comment">    /// &#42; Form != DW&#95;FORM&#95;implicit&#95;const and HasByteSize is true:</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00059" /><CodeLine lineNumber="59"><Highlight kind="comment">    ///     ByteSize contains the fixed size in bytes for the Form in this</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00060" /><CodeLine lineNumber="60"><Highlight kind="comment">    ///     object.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00061" /><CodeLine lineNumber="61"><Highlight kind="comment">    /// &#42; Form != DW&#95;FORM&#95;implicit&#95;const and HasByteSize is false:</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00062" /><CodeLine lineNumber="62"><Highlight kind="comment">    ///     byte size of Form either varies according to the DWARFUnit</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00063" /><CodeLine lineNumber="63"><Highlight kind="comment">    ///     that it is contained in or the value size varies and must be</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00064" /><CodeLine lineNumber="64"><Highlight kind="comment">    ///     decoded from the debug information in order to determine its size.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00065" /><CodeLine lineNumber="65"><Highlight kind="comment">    /// &#42; Form == DW&#95;FORM&#95;implicit&#95;const:</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00066" /><CodeLine lineNumber="66"><Highlight kind="comment">    ///     Value contains value for the implicit&#95;const attribute.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00190" /><CodeLine lineNumber="190"><Highlight kind="comment">    /// The fixed byte size for fixed size forms.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
